      \begin {tikzcd}
        \alpha \ar [dd, mapsto, "(f_*)^*"']\ar [r, mapsto, "\Phi _A"] & \alpha _A(1_A)\ar [d, "Ff"] \\
                                                                & Ff(\alpha _c(1_c))\\
        \alpha  f_*\ar [r, mapsto, "\Phi _B"'] & (\alpha  f_*)_B(1_B)\ar [u, equals]\makebox [0pt][l]{,}
      \end {tikzcd}


where the equality is exactly the final step of the bijectivity proof.

